[package]
name = "clap-sys"
version = "0.5.0"
rust-version = "1.64"
authors = ["Micah Johnston <micah@photophore.systems>", "Robbert van der Helm <mail@robbertvanderhelm.nl"]
edition = "2021"
description = "Rust bindings for the CLAP audio plugin API"
repository = "https://github.com/micahrj/clap-sys"
readme = "README.md"
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]

[package]
name = "nih_plug"
version = "0.0.0"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.80"
authors = ["Robbert van der Helm <mail@robbertvanderhelm.nl>"]
license = "ISC"
keywords = ["audio", "plugin", "vst", "vst3"]
description = "A simple but modern API-agnostic audio plugin framework"
repository = "https://github.com/robbert-vdh/nih-plug"

[workspace]
resolver = "2"
members = ["nih_plug_derive", "nih_plug_egui", "nih_plug_iced", "nih_plug_vizia", "nih_plug_xtask", "cargo_nih_plug", "xtask", "plugins/examples/byo_gui_gl", "plugins/examples/byo_gui_softbuffer", "plugins/examples/byo_gui_wgpu", "plugins/examples/gain", "plugins/examples/gain_gui_egui", "plugins/examples/gain_gui_iced", "plugins/examples/gain_gui_vizia", "plugins/examples/midi_inverter", "plugins/examples/poly_mod_synth", "plugins/examples/sine", "plugins/examples/stft", "plugins/examples/sysex", "plugins/soft_vacuum", "plugins/buffr_glitch", "plugins/crisp", "plugins/crossover", "plugins/diopser", "plugins/loudness_war_winner", "plugins/puberty_simulator", "plugins/safety_limiter", "plugins/spectral_compressor"]

[features]
default = ["vst3"]
assert_process_allocs = ["dep:assert_no_alloc"]
standalone = ["dep:baseview", "dep:clap", "dep:cpal", "dep:jack", "dep:midir", "dep:rtrb"]
vst3 = ["dep:vst3-sys"]
simd = []
zstd = ["dep:zstd"]
docs = []

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0"
anymap3 = "1.0.1"
atomic_float = "0.1"
atomic_refcell = "0.1"
backtrace = "0.3.65"
bitflags = "1.3"
cfg-if = "1.0"
crossbeam = "0.8"
midi-consts = "0.1"
nih_log = "0.3.1"
parking_lot = "0.12"
raw-window-handle = "0.5"
serde_json = "1.0"
widestring = "1.0.0-beta.1"

[dependencies.nih_plug_derive]
path = "nih_plug_derive"

[dependencies.clap-sys]
git = "https://github.com/micahrj/clap-sys.git"
rev = "25d7f53fdb6363ad63fbd80049cb7a42a97ac156"

[dependencies.log]
version = "0.4"
features = ["std", "release_max_level_info"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.assert_no_alloc]
git = "https://github.com/robbert-vdh/rust-assert-no-alloc.git"
branch = "feature/nested-permit-forbid"
features = ["backtrace", "log"]
optional = true

[dependencies.baseview]
git = "https://github.com/RustAudio/baseview.git"
rev = "579130ecb4f9f315ae52190af42f0ea46aeaa4a2"
features = ["opengl"]
optional = true

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.1.8"
features = ["derive", "wrap_help"]
optional = true

[dependencies.cpal]
version = "0.15"
optional = true

[dependencies.jack]
version = "0.11.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.midir]
version = "0.9.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.rtrb]
version = "0.2.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.vst3-sys]
git = "https://github.com/robbert-vdh/vst3-sys.git"
branch = "fix/drop-box-from-raw"
optional = true

[dependencies.zstd]
version = "0.12.3"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies]
approx = "0.5.1"

[target."cfg(all(target_family = \"unix\", not(target_os = \"macos\")))".dependencies]
libc = "0.2.124"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
objc = "0.2.7"
core-foundation = "0.9.3"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.windows]
version = "0.44"
features = ["Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Performance"]

[profile.release]
lto = "thin"
strip = "symbols"

[profile.profiling]
inherits = "release"
debug = true
strip = "none"

[package]
name = "nih_plug_derive"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = ["Robbert van der Helm <mail@robbertvanderhelm.nl>"]
license = "ISC"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
quote = "1.0"
proc-macro2 = "1.0"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "1.0"
features = ["extra-traits"]

[dev-dependencies.nih_plug]
path = ".."
default-features = false

[package]
name = "vst3-com"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["Microsoft Corp.", "Mike Hilgendorf"]
description = "Fork of com-rs\n"
edition = "2018"
license = "MIT"
readme = "./README.md"

[dependencies.vst3-com-macros]
path = "macros"

[package]
name = "vst3-com-macros"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = ["Microsoft Corp."]
edition = "2018"
description = "Forked from com-rs\n\nCOM crate macros\n"
license = "MIT"
autotests = false

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[[test]]
name = "tests"
path = "tests/progress.rs"

[dev-dependencies]
trybuild = "1.0.13"

[dev-dependencies.vst3-com]
path = ".."

[dependencies]
quote = "1.0.3"
proc-macro2 = "1.0.1"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "1.0.5"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.vst3-com-macros-support]
path = "support"

[package]
name = "vst3-com-macros-support"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = ["Microsoft Corp."]
edition = "2018"
description = "Forked from com-rs\n\nSupport library for COM crate macros\n"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
quote = "1.0"
proc-macro2 = "1.0.1"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "1.0.5"
features = ["full"]

[package]
name = "vst3-sys"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["Mike Hilgendorf <mike@hilgendorf.audio>", "Mirko Covizzi <mrkcvzz@gmail.com>"]
license = "GPLv3"
description = "Pure Rust bindings to the VST3 APIs, based on COM. \n"
edition = "2018"

[dependencies.vst3-com]
path = "./com"

[dev-dependencies]
log = "0.4"
simple_logger = "2.1.0"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
widestring = "0.4.0"

[workspace]
members = ["examples/again", "com", "com/macros", "com/macros/support"]

[[example]]
name = "passthru"
crate-type = ["cdylib"]

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/micahrj/clap-sys"]
git = "https://github.com/micahrj/clap-sys"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "25d7f53fdb6363ad63fbd80049cb7a42a97ac156"

[source."https://github.com/robbert-vdh/nih-plug"]
git = "https://github.com/robbert-vdh/nih-plug"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "master"

[source."https://github.com/robbert-vdh/vst3-sys"]
git = "https://github.com/robbert-vdh/vst3-sys"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "fix/drop-box-from-raw"
